com.github.dylon.liblevenshtein.collection.dawg

Class AbstractDawg

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractSet<String>
        • com.github.dylon.liblevenshtein.collection.dawg.AbstractDawg
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDawg<DawgNode>, IFinalFunction<DawgNode>, ITransitionFunction<DawgNode>, Iterable<String>, Collection<String>, Set<String>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SortedDawg

    public abstract class AbstractDawg
extends AbstractSet<String>
implements IDawg<DawgNode>, IFinalFunction<DawgNode>, ITransitionFunction<DawgNode>
    Provides common logic for all my Dawg implementations. Currently, there is only the SortedDawg implementation, but I have plans for other kinds.
    Since:
    2.1.0
